    "description": "<p>Incorporated in 2015,<u><strong> Stag Match Institute (SMI) </strong></u>a member of <a href=\"http://smet.edu.sg/smet-group/\"><u>SMET Group</u></a>. Offering a comprehensive range of <a href=\"https://smtc.smet.edu.sg/our-courses/\">Courses</a> (WSQ &amp; Non-WSQ) to working professionals (individuals or companies), Our courses were designed &amp; crafted by our experienced certified trainers that aims to impart the most updated industry-relevant knowledge to our trainees.<br>\n <br>\n Leveraging on <a href=\"http://smet.edu.sg/smet-group/\">SMET Group</a>‘s successful formula in the education industry (Stag Match Education and Training Group since 2001), Stag Match Institute is poised to expand in the adult learning segment with the group’s support with its extensive resources, excellent &amp; proven track records in the education industry in Singapore.<br>\n <br>\n Stag Match Pte Ltd is a WSQ Training Provider approved by <a href=\"https://www.ssg.gov.sg/wsq.html\"><strong>SkillsFuture</strong></a><a href=\"https://www.ssg.gov.sg/wsq.html\"><strong> Singapore (SSG)</strong></a>.</p>",
